message: Hi Bob, I have a product that I believe would be of great value to you. It's something that I've been carefully developing and I'm confident it can significantly benefit your business. While I can't disclose all the details right now, I'm willing to offer it to you at a special price of $15000. This is a limited-time opportunity, so if you're interested, please let me know. I'm happy to answer any questions you might have.
